{"tid":1631621,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"麥當勞、Apple Store 有三毛帶緊風向要裝修，我屌曬你地老母","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T01:51:48.000Z","uid":292737,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c451a386493c6f29369d4c3e086f536b7f9cd89f","tid":1631621,"uid":292737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"搞老麥搞老麥搞老麥搞老麥<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629412</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6tq2Cp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6tq2Cp.jpg&h=27e4fe80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmBswvz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmBswvz.jpg&h=4a03602a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［APPLE跪低！］蘋果禁止應用程序允許香港抗議者追踪警察的動向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616517</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jzyiC9u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjzyiC9u.jpg&h=0a2abdce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/muoKyMo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmuoKyMo.jpg&h=4aa711fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/12oFRuw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F12oFRuw.jpg&h=c13921cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢幾個月以黎，一直有連登仔帶風向針對麥當勞，最近連 Apple Store 都想裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢啲 post 仲要有幾千個正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好彩前線班勇武手足少上連登，無俾你地班隱性三毛帶到風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無錯，Tim Cook 奶共，而香港 McDonald's 係中資金拱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但罪不致死，使唔使去到裝修？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n得閒裝飾下，門口貼下文宣 poster 咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6c04c628e7ca6970c35ec38f55d294d115ca6739","tid":1631621,"uid":292737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:44.000Z","msg":"得閒裝飾下，門口貼下文宣 poster 咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff86dc63431423fcad4ab2b4defda1c10ca446b","tid":1631621,"uid":294083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1631437/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631437/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n和理非有分工啦！<br />\n入啦大家！"},{"pid":"2562390bcba96dc02d2150c1dba92f72196d99ab","tid":1631621,"uid":292737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"得閒裝飾下，門口貼下文宣 poster 咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80caaf39d922bafee9bb5e20e5c99da9258b2daa","tid":1631621,"uid":292737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:58:09.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ee2095f153f674d0f9161f0cf9e1c302abd4da","tid":1631621,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:58:14.000Z","msg":"［已FC正視聽，求入］金拱門香港除了中信亦有外資<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/162664